transcript:
[Ringing]
Executive: Hello.
Hello.
Hello.
Hello.
Haan ji Monu ji.
Haan ji. Haan namaskar Aadarsh bol raha hu sir India Mart se. Kal baat hui thi aapse yaad hoga.
Ji.
Kal discussion ho nahi paya tha aap online aa nahi paye the. Aapne morning mein time diya tha morning pe bhi aapse baat ho nahi payi. To abhi aap online aap aaoge sir?
Abhi main aapko thodi der mein karta hu call aadhe ghante mein.
Main abhi thoda sa gaadi pe hu.
Koi nahi aadhe ghante aadhe ghante mein time nikal lena sir 5 minute ka theek hai.
Thik hai.
Okay.
